- Však?

349
00:36:18,547 --> 00:36:22,371
Tak poďte bližšie.

350
00:36:23,997 --> 00:36:25,388
Prosím?

351
00:36:27,350 --> 00:36:30,763
- A začnite sa smiať.
- Smiať?

352
00:36:30,763 --> 00:36:34,456
